    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="What happens if I decline a request from a fan?" class="article-title">
          What happens if I decline a request from a fan?
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p><span>If you decline a request, the request will be automatically canceled and the request fee will be fully refunded to your fans.<br><br>Please note that you will not be penalized for declining a request.</span></p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

